comments: Sabonis (IND) briefly grasps Embiid's (PHI) arm but does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Sabonis (IND) makes contact to Embiid's (PHI) body prior to his gather and upward shooting motion.  A personal foul should have been assessed.
Ennis III (PHI) briefly places his arm around Lamb (IND) and removes it off ball.
Embiid (PHI) collapses his forearm against his body while contesting Lamb's (IND) driving shot attempt and maintains a legal guarding position throughout the shot.
Turner (IND) makes marginal contact with Harris' (PHI) body on his shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact with Warren's (IND) arm as he disengages from making clean contact with the ball.
Turner (IND) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Ennis III's (PHI) path.
Ennis III (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball.
Horford (PHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Brogdon's (IND) path.
Ennis III (PHI) makes marginal contact as he firms up in Lamb's (IND) path during the screen.
Brogdon (IND) engages and disengages with Simmons (PHI) during the inbound pass.
Harris (PHI) makes contact with Brogdon's (IND) body during the drive that affects his SQBR.
Harris (PHI) makes contact to Warren's (IND) body which affects his shot attempt.
Turner (IND) places his left hand momentarily on Embiid's (PHI) side and slides his hand off as he deflects the ball with his right hand.
Simmons (PHI) makes hand on ball contact on Warren's (IND) gather.
Simmons (PHI) wraps Turner (IND) and affects his ability to retrieve the inbound pass.
Horford (PHI) makes brief arm to arm contact with Turner (IND) but does not affect his SQBR.
Brogdon (IND) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
Simmons (PHI) commits a take foul on Brogdon (IND).
Turner (IND) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
